Final and best deadline is 02/14/2024 at 6 pm. ************ Welcome to 1323 Morning Avenue, a charming residence nestled in the heart of Baltimore's vibrant community. This delightful home offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience, ideal for modern urban living. As you step into this inviting abode, you are greeted by a warm and welcoming atmosphere. The spacious living area boasts ample natural light, creating a bright and airy ambiance that sets the tone for relaxation and entertainment.  This residence offers 2 bedrooms, each providing a peaceful retreat at the end of the day. The bedrooms are generously sized and offer versatility to accommodate various lifestyles and preferences. The property also includes  bathrooms, designed for both functionality and style. Featuring contemporary fixtures and finishes, the bathrooms offer a serene space to unwind and rejuvenate. Nestled in a desirable location, 1323 Morning Avenue offers convenient access to a host of amenities, including shopping centers, restaurants, parks, and entertainment options. With easy access to major highways and public transportation, commuting to downtown Baltimore or exploring the city's attractions is a breeze.  Don't miss the opportunity to make 1323 Morning Avenue your new home. Schedule a viewing today and experience the comfort and convenience this residence has to offer.
